: International infantry</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t</li>\r\n\r\n        \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n          \r\n          \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li class=\" column-2\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\"  href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/guides/zcvdhyc\">Guide: Britain&#039;s teenage fighters</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t</li>\r\n\r\n        \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n          \r\n          \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li class=\" column-2\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\"  href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01ssfp5\">Clip: A soldier&#039;s song</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t</li>\r\n\r\n                </ul>\r\n             </div>\r\n       </div>\r\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\">$render(\"secondary-top-story\",\"secondary-top-story-1\");</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n  \r\n  \r\n  \r\n  \r\n  \r\n    \r\n  <div id=\"secondary-top-story-3\" class=\"secondary-top-story\">\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"medium-image\">\r\n                    \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\" secondary-story-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1398678986846\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/galleries/p01xtx6f\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74485000/jpg/_74485795_nursing-ambulance_e-k-campbell_250414.jpg\" alt=\"Great Western Railway train\" />In pictures: WW1 hospitals at home</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n        <p>See how iconic and everyday places were used to treat the injured  \t\r\n        <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__27189162\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n              <ul class=\"see-also\">\r\n\r\n                \r\n        \r\n                              \r\n                              \r\n          \r\n          \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li class=\" first-child column-1\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\"  href=\"h